Company Directory

1. Have all company employees appear upon page load

2. Refresh results upon filter input
- Filter should search first name and last name for results

3. Refresh button
- Simply needs to search the database again, keeping search filters in tact

4. Filter button
- Allow user to filter by location and/or department

5. Personnel, departments and locations buttons
- Refresh and adjust the results to show either the employees, departments or locations

6. Add button
- Modal appears allowing user to select to add employee, department or location

7. Edit button
- Modal showing all data related to the selected employee with the option to edit any information (Also for location & department)

8. Delete button
- Modal asking for confirmation (Also for location & department)

